<lb n="1118a06"/><div1 type="jing"><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"></mulu><jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="1118a07"/>
<lb n="1118a08"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="1118002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（西晉…譯））十一字＝（（竺法護譯））四字【宋】【宮】，（（西晉三藏法師竺法護譯））十字【元】【明】，〔西晉…譯〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118002" word-count="11"><lem>西晉月氏國三藏竺法護譯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">竺法護譯</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">西晉三藏法師竺法護譯</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="1118a09"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。與
<lb n="1118a10"/>大比丘眾俱。比丘五百及諸菩薩</p>
<lb n="1118a11"/><p>爾時世尊告諸比丘。將來之世當有比丘。因
<lb n="1118a12"/>有一法不從法化。令法毀滅不得長益。何謂
<lb n="1118a13"/>為一。不護禁戒。不能守心。不修智慧。放逸其
<lb n="1118a14"/>意。唯求<note n="1118003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝華【宮】</note><app n="1118003"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">華</rdg></app>名不順道教。不肯<note n="1118004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勤＝謹【宋】【元】</note><app n="1118004"><lem>勤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">謹</rdg></app>慕度世之
<lb n="1118a15"/>業。是為一事。令法毀滅</p>
<lb n="1118a16"/><p>佛告比丘。復有二事令法毀滅。何謂為二。一
<lb n="1118a17"/>不護禁戒。不攝其心不修智慧。畜妻養子放
<lb n="1118a18"/>心恣意。賈作治<note n="1118005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝產【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝產【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118005"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">產</rdg></app>。以<note n="1118006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">共相＝相供【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">共相＝相供【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118006"><lem>共相</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">相供</rdg></app>活。二伴黨相著。
<lb n="1118a19"/>憎奉法者欲令<note n="1118007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">陷＝墜【宮】</note><app n="1118007"><lem>陷</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">墜</rdg></app>墮。故為言<note n="1118008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">義＝儀【三】，議【宮】</note><note n="1118008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義＝儀【宋】【元】【明】，＝議【宮】</note><app n="1118008"><lem>義</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">儀</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">議</rdg></app>謂之<note n="1118009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諛＝諭【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="1118009"><lem>諛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諭</rdg></app>諂。
<lb n="1118a20"/><note n="1118010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">內＋（私）【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">內＋（私）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118010"><lem>內</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">內私</rdg></app>犯惡<note n="1118011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118011"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。外<note n="1118012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佯＝揚【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佯＝揚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118012"><lem>佯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">揚</rdg></app>清白。是為二事。令法毀
<lb n="1118a21"/>滅</p>
<lb n="1118a22"/><p>佛告<note n="1118013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="1118013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="1118013"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>比丘。復有三事。令法毀滅。何謂為
<lb n="1118a23"/>三。一既不護<note n="1118014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔禁〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔禁〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118014"><lem>禁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="1118015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝病【宋】，〔戒〕－【聖】</note><app n="1118015"><lem>戒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">病</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不能攝心不修<note n="1118016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智慧＝經義【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智慧＝經義【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118016"><lem>智慧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">經義</rdg></app>。二
<lb n="1118a24"/><note n="1118017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝白【聖】</note><app n="1118017"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">白</rdg></app>讀文字不<note n="1118018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">識＝諦【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">識＝諦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118018"><lem>識</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">諦</rdg></app>句<note n="1118019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逗＝讀【宋】</note><app n="1118019"><lem>逗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">讀</rdg></app>。以上著下以下著上。
<lb n="1118a25"/>頭尾顛倒不能解了義之所歸。自以為是。三
<lb n="1118a26"/>明者呵之不從其教反懷瞋恨。謂相嫉&CB00107;。<note n="1118020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">識義＝議識【聖】</note><app n="1118020"><lem>識
<lb n="1118a27"/>義</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">議識</rdg></app>者少。多不別理<note n="1118021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咸＝成【元】</note><app n="1118021"><lem>咸</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app><note n="1118022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝自【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云＝自【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118022"><lem>云</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg></app>為是。是為三事。令
<lb n="1118a28"/>法毀滅</p>
<lb n="1118a29"/><p>佛告<anchor id="fxT12p1118a01"/>諸比丘。復有四事。令法毀滅。何謂為
<pb n="1118b" id="T12.0395.1118b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118b01"/>四。一將來比丘<note n="1118023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（已捨…業））十二字＝（（捨空閑處修道之業））八字【聖】</note><app n="1118023" word-count="12"><lem>已捨家<note n="1118024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔業〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔業〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118024"><lem>業</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>在空閑處不修
<lb n="1118b02"/>道業</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">捨空閑處修道之業</rdg></app>。二&CB00540;遊人間憒&CB00436;之中行<note n="1118025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">來＋（比丘）【三】【聖】</note><note n="1118025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來＋（比丘）【宋】【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="1118025"><lem>來</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">來比丘</rdg></app>談言。求好
<lb n="1118b03"/>袈裟五色之服。三高<note n="1118026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聽＝望【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聽＝望【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118026"><lem>聽</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">望</rdg></app>遠視以為綺<note n="1118027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雅＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雅＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118027"><lem>雅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飾</rdg></app>。自
<lb n="1118b04"/>以高德無能及者。以雜<note n="1118028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">碎＋（之）【元】【明】</note><app n="1118028"><lem>碎</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">碎之</rdg></app>智<note n="1118029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔比〕－【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118029"><lem>比</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>日月<note n="1118030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之明＝比丘【宋】，之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><note n="1118030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之明＝比丘【宋】，＝之比丘【元】，〔之明〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118030"><lem>之明</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">比丘</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">之比丘</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="1118b05"/>畜已。四不攝三事。不護根門。行婦女間。宣文
<lb n="1118b06"/>飾辭。多言合<note n="1118031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">偶＝禍【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118031"><lem>偶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">禍</rdg></app>。以動人心。使清變濁。身行
<lb n="1118b07"/>荒亂。正法廢遲。是為四事。令法毀滅</p>
<lb n="1118b08"/><p>佛告比丘。復有五事。令法毀滅。何謂為五。
<lb n="1118b09"/><note n="1118032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118032"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>或有比丘。本以法故出家修道。廢深經教
<lb n="1118b10"/>十二因緣三十七品。方等深妙玄虛之慧。智
<lb n="1118b11"/>度無極。善權方便。空無相願至化之<note n="1118033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">節＝第【聖】</note><app n="1118033"><lem>節</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">第</rdg></app>。二
<lb n="1118b12"/>反習雜句淺<note n="1118034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔末〕－【宮】</note><app n="1118034"><lem>末</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>小<note n="1118035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（輩）【宮】</note><app n="1118035"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">經輩</rdg></app>。世俗行故。<note n="1118036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝三【三】</note><note n="1118036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝三【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118036"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三</rdg></app>者經典
<lb n="1118b13"/>亂道之原。好講此業。易解世事。趣得人心令
<lb n="1118b14"/>其歡<note n="1118037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝悅【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜＝悅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118037"><lem>喜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悅</rdg></app>。因致名聞<note n="1118038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔三〕－【宋】【宮】，三＝四【元】【明】</note><app n="1118038"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app>新聞法人。淺解之士
<lb n="1118b15"/>意用妙快。深達之<note n="1118039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">士＝人【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">士＝人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118039"><lem>士</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>不用為<note n="1118040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佳＝法【聖】</note><app n="1118040"><lem>佳</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>。<note n="1118041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔四〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118041"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>天龍鬼
<lb n="1118b16"/>神不以為喜。心懷悒慼口<note n="1118042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">發斯＝能發【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">發斯＝能發【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118042"><lem>發斯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">能發</rdg></app>言。大法欲滅
<lb n="1118b17"/>故使其然。捨妙<note n="1118043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法化＝化法【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法化＝化法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118043"><lem>法化</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">化法</rdg></app>反宣雜句。諸天流淚速
<lb n="1118b18"/>逝而去。五<note n="1118044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">由＋（說）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">由＋（說）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118044"><lem>由</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">由說</rdg></app>是正法稍稍見捨無精修者。是
<lb n="1118b19"/>為五事。令法毀滅</p>
<lb n="1118b20"/><p>佛告比丘。吾滅度後。有此邪事十<note n="1118045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五＝四【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五＝四【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118045"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app>之亂令
<lb n="1118b21"/>法毀滅。一何痛哉。若有比丘欲諦學道。棄捐
<lb n="1118b22"/>綺飾不求名聞。質<note n="1118046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">朴＝科【三】</note><note n="1118046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">朴＝科【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="1118046"><lem>朴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">科</rdg></app>守真宣傳正經。佛之雅
<lb n="1118b23"/>典深法之<note n="1118047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化＝辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118047"><lem>化</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">辭</rdg></app>不用多言。案<note n="1118048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">本說＝其本【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本說＝其本【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118048"><lem>本說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">其本</rdg></app>經不捨正
<lb n="1118b24"/>句。希言屢中不失佛意。&CB00308;衣趣食。得美不甘
<lb n="1118b25"/>得&CB00308;不<note n="1118049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝&CB01158;【宋】【宮】</note><app n="1118049"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB01158;</rdg></app>。衣食好醜隨施者意不以瞋喜。
<lb n="1118b26"/><note n="1118050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">攝＝護【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攝＝護【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118050"><lem>攝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">護</rdg></app>身口意守諸根門不違佛教。<note n="1118051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝壽【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝壽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118051"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">壽</rdg></app>命甚<note n="1118052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矩＝短【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="1118052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矩＝短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="1118052"><lem>矩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">短</rdg></app>
<lb n="1118b27"/>恍<note n="1118053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惚＝忽【聖】</note><app n="1118053"><lem>惚</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">忽</rdg></app><note n="1118054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118054"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>過。如夢所見覺不知<note n="1118055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">處＝虛【宋】</note><app n="1118055"><lem>處</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">虛</rdg></app>。三塗之難
<lb n="1118b28"/>不可稱計。勤修佛法猶救頭然。五戒十善六
<lb n="1118b29"/>度無極。四等四恩智慧善權。咸可<note n="1118056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">精＝修【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">精＝修【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118056"><lem>精</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">修</rdg></app>行。<note n="1118057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雖＋（復後生）【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雖＋（復後生）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118057"><lem>雖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雖復後生</rdg></app>
<pb n="1118c" id="T12.0395.1118c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1118c01"/>不值佛世出家為道學不唐捐。<note n="1118058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＝卒【宮】</note><app n="1118058"><lem>平</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">卒</rdg></app>其本心愍
<lb n="1118c02"/><note n="1118059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝哀【三】【宮】</note><note n="1118059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝哀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="1118059"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">哀</rdg></app>一切十方蒙恩。佛說如是。諸比丘悲喜前
<lb n="1118c03"/>自歸佛。作禮而去</p>
<lb n="1118c04"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><title>佛說當來變經</title></jhead></juan></div1>
